  "caption": "帶著家人自在的走在街上 感受這座城市最真實的日常 或許 就是這些平凡的時刻 讓丹麥成了我會想再回來的地方 \n（謝謝女兒殿下裡阿ken叔叔替我們的捕捉📸）\nWalking through the streets of Denmark with my family, completely at ease, with nowhere we needed to be.\nMaybe it’s these quiet, simple moments that make Denmark a place I’ll always want to come back to. #dänemark #københavn",
